VS Code-ல 2 Files Create பண்ணு
File 1 → variables.tf
variable "region" {
  description = "AWS Region"
  type        = string
  default     = "ap-south-1"
}

variable "bucket_name" {
  description = "S3 Bucket பேரு"
  type        = string
  default     = "my-app-frontend-2024"
}

variable "environment" {
  description = "dev or prod"
  type        = string
  default     = "dev"
}
File 2 → main.tf
provider "aws" {
  region = var.region
}

resource "aws_s3_bucket" "frontend" {
  bucket = var.bucket_name

  tags = {
    Environment = var.environment
    Name        = "Frontend Bucket"
  }
}
Terminal-ல Run பண்ணு
terraform plan
Output இப்படி வரும்:
+ bucket      = "my-app-frontend-2024"
+ environment = "dev"

Plan: 1 to add ✅
PHASE 2 — Outputs கத்துக்கோ
என்னதுக்கு Outputs?
Create ஆன பிறகு — URL, ARN, ID
இதை automatically print பண்ண
File 3 → outputs.tf
output "bucket_name" {
  description = "Bucket பேரு"
  value       = aws_s3_bucket.frontend.bucket
}

output "bucket_arn" {
  description = "Bucket ARN"
  value       = aws_s3_bucket.frontend.arn
}
Terminal-ல Run பண்ணு:
terraform apply
Apply complete!

Outputs:
bucket_name = "my-app-frontend-2024"    ✅
bucket_arn  = "arn:aws:s3:::my-app..."  ✅
PHASE 3 — Full Project Structure
இப்போ உன் folder இப்படி இருக்கணும்:
terraform-learn/
├── main.tf          ← Resources
├── variables.tf     ← Variables
├── outputs.tf       ← Outputs
└── .terraform/      ← Auto created (touch பண்ணாத)
PHASE 4 — EC2 Add பண்ணுவோம்
variables.tf — இதை add பண்ணு:
variable "instance_type" {
  description = "EC2 size"
  type        = string
  default     = "t2.micro"
}
main.tf — EC2 add பண்ணு:
# EC2 Instance
resource "aws_instance" "backend" {
  ami           = "ami-0f5ee92e2d63afc18"  # Ubuntu 22.04
  instance_type = var.instance_type

  tags = {
    Name        = "Backend-Server"
    Environment = var.environment
  }
}
outputs.tf — EC2 output add பண்ணு:
output "ec2_public_ip" {
  description = "Backend Server IP"
  value       = aws_instance.backend.public_ip
}
